race.description: Ladbrokes Racing Extras In Multi Mdn Hcp
race.comment: COMBAT CRUSADER (1) hasn't been too far away in all three runs this preparation and this is not an overly strong affair. Ready to peak now fourth-up from the break and should be right there when the whips are cracking. OUTONO (2) has gotten better with each career effort and looks to be working up towards a maiden victory. Gets the services of Wiggins in the irons and will make his presence felt. FLOURISH (5) placed around this circuit last time out and rates among the top-three hopes again. URIS (4) has hit the top-five in ten of 11 starts and is usually thereabouts. A must for the multiples. TRUSTING STAR (9) next in line from the inside marble.
